{"tid":898802,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"深田恭子36歲生日「色氣全開」 穿這樣約會龜梨和也","createTime":"2018-11-12T02:42:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-14T02:16:30.000Z","uid":9573,"like":290,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":92,"replies":[{"pid":"fbd9c5befc75b2eeaa30aa36be48aa650c3d4f02","tid":898802,"uid":9573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-12T02:42:41.000Z","msg":"日本女星深田恭子與小3歲傑尼斯偶像龜梨和也，低調談姐弟戀近3年，感情超甜蜜，近日她被直擊一身性感露香肩的打扮，與一票演藝圈好友歡慶36歲生日，正當大家都在找尋龜梨和也身影時，才知道原來他早就在裡面等待，派對過後與與深田恭子一同甜蜜離去。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.chinatimes.com/newsphoto/2018-11-08/656/20181108004782.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.chinatimes.com%2Fnewsphoto%2F2018-11-08%2F656%2F20181108004782.jpg&h=ac93f3da&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n深田恭子、龜梨和也因合作電視劇擦愛火。<br />\n<br />\n深田恭子36歲前一天，相約西川貴教等好友前往東京六本木某會員制法國餐廳歡慶36歲生日，雖然狗仔沒拍到男友龜梨和也的照片，但據知情人士透露，其實龜梨和也早就在餐廳裡面等待，小倆口之後一起甜蜜離開。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.chinatimes.com/newsphoto/2018-11-08/656/20181108004781.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.chinatimes.com%2Fnewsphoto%2F2018-11-08%2F656%2F20181108004781.jpg&h=221cf439&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/ent/page/800/2018/08/27/phps63EnY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fent%2Fpage%2F800%2F2018%2F08%2F27%2Fphps63EnY.jpg&h=2a602dea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://www.hkcnews.com/news_%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/hk-discuss/2018/11/%E6%B6%88%E9%98%B2%E8%99%95-CPR%E5%BF%83%E8%82%BA%E5%BE%A9%E7%94%A6%E6%B3%95-%E4%BB%BB%E4%BD%95%E4%BB%81-20181106150846_2c8a_large.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcnews.com%2Fnews_%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2Fhk-discuss%2F2018%2F11%2F%25E6%25B6%2588%25E9%2598%25B2%25E8%2599%2595-CPR%25E5%25BF%2583%25E8%2582%25BA%25E5%25BE%25A9%25E7%2594%25A6%25E6%25B3%2595-%25E4%25BB%25BB%25E4%25BD%2595%25E4%25BB%2581-20181106150846_2c8a_large.jpg&h=6364ab88&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n深田恭子性感露香肩，歡慶36歲生日。<br />\n<br />\n而深田恭子當天露出白嫩香肩的﻿嘉亨灣海景兩房2.45萬性感裝扮，更獲網友一致好評，大讚她屬兩房間隔，望海景，「色氣全開」，意指她性感魅力爆棚、女人味十足，認為深田恭子也太適合穿黑色了吧。"},{"pid":"eff0048db312bce8dbb3c707d40c62edf0c0399e","tid":898802,"uid":4180,"like":83,"dislike":2,"score":81,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-12T02:43:13.000Z","msg":"仲係好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d5de8dce08f70e0db47d7518115e16399d795b3","tid":898802,"uid":122139,"like":390,"dislike":4,"score":386,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-12T02:45:10.000Z","msg":"而深田恭子當天露出白嫩香肩的﻿嘉亨灣海景兩房2.45萬性感裝扮，更獲網友一致好評，大讚她屬兩房間隔，望海景，<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b54a31f4fcdadb96c713438e002eae282e70149","tid":898802,"uid":70301,"like":178,"dislike":6,"score":172,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-12T02:45:19.000Z","msg":"乜36歲㗎咋？<br />\n我記得好細個聽過佢名<br />\n伽利略客串其中一集嗰陣重以為佢年紀好大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申：90前"},{"pid":"d90bc20aa3cfc74897c08cb780cd2356247a3419","tid":898802,"uid":76063,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-12T02:46:32.000Z","msg":"正撚到"},{"pid":"f0ffd02ac897cb8efc536407e048a90d0e19df38","tid":898802,"uid":46500,"like":14,"dislike":11,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-12T02:47:09.000Z","msg":"最後面做乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65979a1b41e6b8df08928fee15535dfac6339d35","tid":898802,"uid":22029,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-12T02:47:22.000Z","msg":"當年下妻物語真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10215ec7d80c99b10d118e6902ff2d726112b55b","tid":898802,"uid":219529,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-1